7. Channel Strategy & Sales Motion — direct vs partner, AE capacity, sales cycle (include horizontalBar chart: channel revenue potential $M)
8. Pricing Architecture — land-and-expand model, benchmark vs peers
[SECTION: Execution & Financials]
9. Marketing & Demand Generation — CAC by channel, pipeline coverage ratio
10. Launch Roadmap — phased 18-month plan with owners (include horizontalBar chart: phase timeline by quarter)
11. Financial Projections — 3-year ARR, gross margin, EBITDA (include bar chart: ARR and EBITDA $M by year)
