4. Performance Benchmarking — KPIs vs best-in-class peers (include bar chart: performance score by dimension vs benchmark)
[SECTION: Root Cause Analysis]
5. Current State Assessment — 5-dimension capability scan: people, process, technology, data, governance
6. Root Cause Analysis — MECE issue tree, systemic vs symptomatic causes
7. Value Leakage Identification — where EBITDA is being lost (include bar chart: value at stake $M by lever)
8. Organizational Capability Assessment — talent gaps, decision rights, span of control
[SECTION: Recommendations]
9. Technology & Process Maturity — current vs target state, gap analysis
10. Financial Performance Deep-Dive — EBITDA bridge (include bar chart: EBITDA bridge current to potential $M)
11. Strategic Options — fix, divest, transform with NPV scenarios
12. Priority Opportunities — ranked by impact and ease of implementation
13. Recommended Roadmap — 3-horizon plan with investment requirements
14. Return on Investment Summary — total value at stake, net investment, payback period',
  investor: '[SECTION: The Opportunity]
1. Title
2. Executive Summary — investment thesis: problem, solution, traction, ask
3. The Problem — market pain, frequency, who suffers, why now
